data.name: btnGetMovieInfo.ToolTip
data.value:
[ALT-G] Gets TMDb/OMDb movie info for selected rows or current row. If the movie has a valid IMDB ID, it is used to find a match. Otherwise, the movie Title and Year are used to find the most likely match.
SHIFT+Click to bypass Cache (force online search) CTRL+Click to allow overwriting existing values with blanks
